Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.45,Default,Turban,0000,0000,0000,,Thằng thầy tu chó chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.37,Default,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,Siêu-thầy tu chứ.
